      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/money-fund-assets-fall-for-second-week-on-portfolio-reallocation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者在新的一年里继续重新分配投资组合，货币市场基金资产连续第二周下跌，主要是机构基金资产撤离。]]></description>
